title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre possibly giving too much airtime to your critics and not enough to your allies now. However, its easy to obsess over detractors because you may believe that if you prove them wrong, you can stand victorious and happy with your work. Unfortunately, you still might be embracing the wrong lesson today. Simply jumping through hoops for others wont be enough to satisfy your high standards. You are the single most important judge of yourself and the good deeds you do. Be a warrior, not a worrier. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
